@uranusjr It looks like the latest pipenv version 2018.5.13 will recreate virtualenv somehow when there are editable packages in pipefile.

And it will generates ```parsel = {ref = "f6103c8", git = "https://github.com/scrapy/parsel.git", editable = true} ``` instead of ```parsel = {git = "https://github.com/scrapy/parsel.git@f6103c8", editable = true}```

So if you are locking by ```parsel = {git = "https://github.com/scrapy/parsel.git@f6103c8", editable = true}``` while pipenv will lock by ```parsel = {ref = "f6103c8", git = "https://github.com/scrapy/parsel.git", editable = true} ```. Then the hashes will be different...

